data.description: JUST REDUCED- BEAUTIFULLY MAINTAINED, spacious 3/2/2 with lots of extras- office, LARGE bonus room off garage and kitchen which could be converted to apartment or mother-in-law suite, hot tub, 2 storage sheds, space for a boat or RV parking, all on oversized lot! Convenient to everything Port Charlotte has to offer! Updated kitchen has granite counters, island, newer appliances. Washroom off kitchen leads to big bonus room and storage closet/possible future bathroom, and separate entrance in garage. Living room has expansive window walls and working fireplace. Bedroom 2 has HUGE walk in closet; bedroom 3 has interior and exterior entrance. Bathrooms have been updated. Well maintained yard with patio, hot tub and storage sheds. AC installed 2017. Use AS-IS contract with proof of funds and pre-approval. Information deemed reliable but not guaranteed.
